author: alally
msg: Be sure to clone metadata before UimaCppAnalysisComponent makes modifications to it.
UimaCppAnalysisComponent was nulling out the fsIndexCollection part of the metadata
before sending to C++, which should be OK if done on a clone.  Without the clone it
was deleting the index for everyone, affecting CAS creation.
